{"tid":1862410,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"遭網友狠酸不顧疫情 羅志祥女友曬「捐款收據」打臉反嗆","createTime":"2020-02-04T15:15:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-04T15:20:35.000Z","uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4d8506d384e7e475ecca99a5dbb52ec2e4b7f5a5","tid":1862410,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T15:15:43.000Z","msg":"遭網友狠酸不顧疫情 羅志祥女友曬「捐款收據」打臉反嗆<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/nKIc8POaV4uPCxNsMcuGOg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/entertainment.nownews.hk/7c212e5213fa072bed02b286fb490b1f\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FnKIc8POaV4uPCxNsMcuGOg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fentertainment.nownews.hk%2F7c212e5213fa072bed02b286fb490b1f&h=7a5d9ae3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n武漢肺炎疫情失控，各地民眾人心惶惶，許多藝人透過捐款、口罩等物資來替正面臨危機的武漢盡一份心力，明星或網紅若沒有透過社群平台表達關切，很有可能會引來網友不滿。羅志祥的女友周揚青擁有出眾的外貌，近日她在IG上大秀舞技，未料卻遭網友開嗆未關心疫情，周揚青則是不客氣地直接曬捐款收據回打臉。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/JkOJdKnXEEeAMvlSZmHpAw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTk5O2g9NzU5/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/entertainment.nownews.hk/3606ade8345d63dab99b4256f1f1c9d9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FJkOJdKnXEEeAMvlSZmHpAw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTk5O2g9NzU5%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fentertainment.nownews.hk%2F3606ade8345d63dab99b4256f1f1c9d9&h=60b837d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲周揚青時常與粉絲們分享生活點滴。（圖／翻攝IG）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n網紅周揚青與天王羅志祥交往多年，小倆口感情穩定，目前已經毫不掩飾地在社群網站公開放閃，現在正值武漢肺炎防疫的關鍵時期，周揚青一如往常地向粉絲分享生活點滴，大秀舞技，不過1名網友私訊她：「你是真不知道武漢現在是什麼狀況還是覺得事不關己？還有心情在那邊像個白痴一樣地轉圈圈？」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n周揚青收到訊息之後相當傻眼，PO出網友的截圖並公開帳號於限時動態：「媽呀我一定是太閒了，不然怎麼都開始曬智障？這種人微博有，抖音有就算了，怎麼ins也開始有了... 」隨後曬出她自己捐款10萬元人民幣的收據，並回嗆該民網友：「老子在捐錢捐物資的時候，你除了到處罵人道德綁架。」最後氣到乾脆公開慈善基機會的帳號再嗆：「那我也來道德綁架你一下，去給老子捐錢去。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/9VIiHsZmOp3O9FYCjQRF6A--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NDE5O2g9ODEx/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/entertainment.nownews.hk/226e9e1b79f2cac004b467e1fc7a81d0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F9VIiHsZmOp3O9FYCjQRF6A--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NDE5O2g9ODEx%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fentertainment.nownews.hk%2F226e9e1b79f2cac004b467e1fc7a81d0&h=6505b8f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲周揚青遭網友酸未關心疫情。（圖／翻攝IG）<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/y6nKpENJHLTzvb4CZ6OScQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NDE5O2g9ODAw/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/entertainment.nownews.hk/6bb42299462dc11003a482589604e7c9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fy6nKpENJHLTzvb4CZ6OScQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NDE5O2g9ODAw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fentertainment.nownews.hk%2F6bb42299462dc11003a482589604e7c9&h=c8e1ae01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲周揚青曬捐款收據。（圖／翻攝IG）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n事實上， 前鎮子美國湖人隊前球星Kobe Bryant不幸過世時，知名Youtuber愛莉莎莎也曾因為沒有發文悼念而遭網友出征，愛莉莎莎則回應：「平常沒在看籃球，在看到訊息之前也不知道Kobe死了，是要關心什麼？」她表示對於Kobe逝世備感遺憾，不過現在自己比較關心將會死更多人，和她息息相關的武漢肺炎，愛莉莎莎的高EQ回應隨後大獲好評。（編輯：侯家瑜）"},{"pid":"f293584931e04d0cdc9cdbc030cf18a867b97d65","tid":1862410,"uid":297212,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T15:20:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">這種人微博有，抖音有就算了，怎麼ins也開始有了</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}